  "text": "Both user profile and product information have crucial effects on sentiment polarities. [CITATION_1] proposed a model by incorporating user and product information into a CNN network for document level sentiment classification. User ids and product names are included as features in a unified document vector using the vector space model such that document vectors capture important global clues include individual preferences and product information.",
